I"1<p>Azure Portal Tips &amp; Tricks is a series of short videos where I am showing various features of the Azure Portal and how you can take advantage of them to be more productive.</p>
<p>On the Azure Portal you can create already configured Virtual Machines, e.g. for node or ruby development, or with the latest Visual Studio and .NET Core installed. In this video I am showing how to create VM with MEAN stack installed, how to create an express app, and run it within 5 minutes.</p>
